   617вҶ’
   618вҶ’You may pull in just the part of this semver utility that you need if you
   619вҶ’are sensitive to packing and tree-shaking concerns.  The main
   620вҶ’`require('semver')` export uses getter functions to lazily load the parts
   621вҶ’of the API that are used.
   622вҶ’
   623вҶ’The following modules are available:
   624вҶ’
   625вҶ’* `require('semver')`
   626вҶ’* `require('semver/classes')`
   627вҶ’* `require('semver/classes/comparator')`
   628вҶ’* `require('semver/classes/range')`
   629вҶ’* `require('semver/classes/semver')`
   630вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/clean')`
   631вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/cmp')`
   632вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/coerce')`
   633вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/compare')`
   634вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/compare-build')`
   635вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/compare-loose')`
   636вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/diff')`
   637вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/eq')`
   638вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/gt')`
   639вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/gte')`
   640вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/inc')`
   641вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/lt')`
   642вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/lte')`
   643вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/major')`
   644вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/minor')`
   645вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/neq')`
   646вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/parse')`
   647вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/patch')`
   648вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/prerelease')`
   649вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/rcompare')`
   650вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/rsort')`
   651вҶ’* `require('semver/functions/satisfies')`
